snippet.title: Super Monkey Ball Banana Mania | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to go bananas! 🍌

Super Monkey Ball Banana Mania brings the series back to its beginnings for Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, and Steam this October 5th!

#SuperMonkeyBall #BananaMania #SMB20th
